# 📊 Workflow

```
Start Program
      │
      ▼
Read PID
      │
      ▼
Open /proc/<pid>/status
      │
      ▼
Display Process Information
      │
      ▼
Open /proc/<pid>/maps
      │
      ▼
Parse Memory Regions
      │
      ▼
Classify Sections
      │
      ▼
Display Memory Layout
      │
      ▼
Exit
```

